The Duke is reportedly "worried sick" his highly anticipated memoir "will lead to a new war with the royals". The source told Heat magazine that "Meghan is urging him to tell his truth and not hide what really happened" while he struggles with what to include. They added: "Every passage is being revised again and again. Harry keeps remembering new things he wants to include, and then suddenly panics about toning down certain anecdotes." FOLLOW BELOW FOR UPDATES...